Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent

Class ListServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent.ListServiceFluent<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.Insertion
public class ListServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends Object implements io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.Insertion
Fluent service for interacting with list UI elements.

Provides methods for selecting, validating, and interacting with lists in a structured manner.

The generic type T represents the UI service fluent implementation that extends UiServiceFluent, allowing method chaining for seamless interaction.
